# Trivy vulnerability waivers.
#
# Each entry is a CVE we have reviewed and consciously accept, with the reason.
# Keep this list short and revisit it when the base image is updated.

# CVE-2026-12151 — undici DoS via unbounded WebSocket memory growth.
# Present only in the undici bundled *inside npm* in the node:24-slim base image
# (usr/local/lib/node_modules/npm/node_modules/undici), NOT a proxy dependency
# and not on the proxy's runtime path (npm is not invoked at runtime). Fixable
# only upstream when node:24-slim ships a newer bundled npm. Reviewed 2026-07-12.
CVE-2026-12151
